# ftaxi: Faraday FTAXIC030 AXI Fabric
# FTAXIC030 provides a high-performance AXI bus controller with a highly
# configurable and flexibly programmable model to ease the effort of AXI
# SoC creation. FTAXIC030 implements an infrastructure of an AXI-based
# system with a matrix topology connection. The AXI fabric has 4
# masters: PCIe (M0), USB (M1), WDMA (M2), ARM (M3). The AXI fabric has
# 5 slaves: PCIe DBI, USB, PCIe SLV, BF, AHBF. Generally, no registers
# in this block should be changed.
