# ftaxi STAREG: AXI IC Status Register
# When the APB interface receives a non-existing address, AXI IC will
# respond error (PslvErr) and set the APBDecErr flag. The error response
# (PslvErr) can be disabled by DisAPBSlvErr register but the APB error
