# Max_Payload_Size, and speed. The value is determined from Tables 3-7,
# 3-8, and 3-9 of the PCIe 3.0 specification. The limit must reflect the
# round trip latency from requester to completer. If there is a change
# in the payload size or link width, the controller will override any
# value that you have written to this register field, and reset the
