# AUTOACQALLTIME: 
# Access RW
# Normal mode Power-saving option. when set, ADC continuously acquires
# data as long as pmon_enable is asserted, although it uses configured
# number of samples for calculating pmon average from pmon_start rising-
# edge. Default value is 0, acquires configured number of samples and
